-- TDD red-step bucket. Hosts assertions that capture intended
-- post-fix behavior before the implementation lands. Tests here
-- are expected to fail on the current builder and pass once the
-- corresponding green-step task ships. NOT part of the default
-- gate (`nix build .#checks.unit` / `just unit` / `just ci`); run
-- with `just red` or `cabal test red-tests` to see the executable
-- red proof.
